Command: search
Description: Searches the framework for exploits, payloads, or targets.

Usage:
    search exploits [keyword] - Search modules by path, name, CVE, or description.
    search payloads [keyword] - Search available payloads.
    search recon [keyword] - List all configured targets and ports.

Example:
    search exploits dirtypipe
    search payloads windows
    search recon fingerprint